title: Watch Harley Quinn Get Mashed Up With Lady Gaga in This Musical 'Suicide Squad' Parody
text:
Tweet Posted: Thu, 3/16/2017 - 10:13pm by Editor 
Hilly and Hannah Hindi have been around YouTube for years now, and are mostly known for their parodies of popular nerd-culture favorites like Supernatural , Dr. Who , and Sherlock . They only release their big videos a few times a year, but they really go all out with their costumes, makeup, production design, and choreography. Their latest is called Suicide Squad Parody , which is the perfect name for a parody of 2016’s hit movie, Suicide Squad . Not content to make fun of one thing at a time, the girls are also parodying Lady Gaga’s 2011 hit song/video, Judas . Check it out. 
Just to give some perspective, here’s Lady Gaga’s video for Judas . They really nail the look, right? 
Hilly and Hannah also nailed their scenes from Suicide Squad . @HillywoodShow IT LOOKS THE SAME AS THE MOVIE OMG pic.twitter.com/I0G81d31Cw
